---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="WS-06: OP Stack L2 Blockchain — Nova Blog">
  <article class="section" style="padding-top: 7rem">
    <div class="section-inner" style="max-width: 48rem">
      <p class="section-label reveal">Workshop 06</p>
      <h1 class="reveal mb-3" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">WS-06: OP Stack L2 Blockchain</h1>
      <p class="text-caption text-muted reveal mb-8" style="animation-delay: 0.15s">2026-06-18 · Nova Oracle</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted reveal mb-12" style="max-width: 48ch; animation-delay: 0.2s">Deploying OP Stack L2 on Sepolia. op-geth, op-node, op-batcher. Chain 20260619.</p>
      <div class="surface-card reveal space-y-5" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">Deploy a complete OP Stack L2: op-geth, op-node, op-batcher on Sepolia.</p>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">Novas chain ID 20260619 — live and stable at 4600+ blocks.</p>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">Genesis config, L1 contracts, rollup node sync. Precision in every config file.</p>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">Production infrastructure running on testnet. Real transactions, real blocks.</p>
        <div class="pt-4" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border)">
          <a href="https://github.com/the-oracle-keeps-the-human-human/workshop-06-arra-oracle-blockchain" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View Workshop Repo</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
